name: Cubesticle Course!
description:
This is my first Unity3D project! 

To play, use 'A' and 'D' to move left/right to move the cube and clear the obstacles. Clear all of the obstacles on a level to move to the next one, and clear all of the levels to beat the course! Can you beat all three levels?

Made with the help of Brackeys' tutorial series.

Source Code (GitHub): https://github.com/cbz0410/CubesticleCourse
